profile:
Enviro Masters Lawn Care is a Canadian owned company and has been serving the Kingston area since 1994. It currently manages 1300 Kingston homes annually.  
Since its inception it has been on the cutting edge of change. 

Our goal is to continually improve the soil by using top quality products such as organic fertilizers (versus synthetic) and compost. We provide better and healthier lawns.

We begin by meeting with you at your home.  Then we perform a personalized lawn care analysis and consultation.  Finally, we will suggest one of our programs that will best suit your lawn.

Our services include: full lawn programs, organic fertilizing, weed and crabgrass control, lawn rolling, dethatching, aeration, machine overseeding, topdressing,  soil conditioning, power sweeping, and insect control.
